name: Searchtree
body:
### Introduction
Purpose of this project is find paths for obstacle navigation using uninformed and informed symbolic search.Various type of search methods are implemented such as [Breadth-first,Depth-first](http://youtu.be/nzGSoiGbFig),[Uniform Cost](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IizKzkVQ2iA&feature=share&list=PLF236785979DFDDE6),[Greedy best-first](http://youtu.be/XYYkjjZchRM),[A* algorithm](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_CBhTubi-CU).

 
### Report

You can find more details at the report which is hosted at repository.

### Deployment

Project run environment

windows 7 - javaSE 1.6 ubuntu 12 - javaSE 1.6

* [import](http://help.eclipse.org/juno/index.jsp?topic=%2Forg.eclipse.platform.doc.user%2Ftasks%2Ftasks-importproject.htm) the project into eclipse

* fill destination and starting point and choose algorithm , algortihm will give output on labels and text field

### Support or Contact
if you have any questions please reach me via [my personal page](www.eldemcando.com).
